room_title: Escape room "Island Escape" by Breakout Games - Baltimore in Baltimore
review: Great escape room! Had so much fun! I've done two here so far and plan to do more escape rooms in the future!

room_title: Escape room "Island Escape" by Breakout Games - Baltimore in Baltimore
review: We love the Breakout games in Columba so we tried to give the Timonium location a try. The Island Escape room was really fun and we had a great time! The staff was very friendly as well!

room_title: Escape room "Island Escape" by Breakout Games - Baltimore in Baltimore
review: By far the best experience I've had doing escape rooms. The staff was friendly and welcoming. We did two rooms in one day, and both were very well planned out. The volcano room was amazing!
